    <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
        <body>
            <div xml:id="KT395-kilavi">
                <p type="edition">varaiviṭai vaittup piriya āṟṟāḷākiya kiḻatti “nām āṇṭuc cēṟum”
                    eṉat tōḻikku uraittatu. </p>


                <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">Told to the confidante, saying “we are going
                    there!” by HER, who doesn”t have the strength [anymore], when [he] separates
                    after the time of marriage has been fixed. </p>
            </div>

            <div xml:id="KT395">
                <lg type="edition">
                    <l> neñcē niṟaiyol lātē yavarē</l>
                    <l> yaṉpiṉ maiyi ṉaruḷporu ḷeṉṉār</l>
                    <l> vaṉkaṇ koṇṭu valittuval lunarē</l>
                    <l> yaravuṟu matiyiṟ kivaṇōr pōlak</l>
                    <l> kaḷaiyā rāyiṉuṅ kaṇṇiṉitu paṭīiya</l>
                    <l> rañca leṉmaru millai yanti</l>
                    <l> laḷitō tāṉē nāṇē</l>
                    <l> yāṅkavar vativayi ṉīṅkap paṭiṉē.</l>


                </lg>

                <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
                    <l> The heart, stopping is impossible [to it].</l>
                    <l rend="indent9"> He,</l>
                    <l>without saying “[even] if there is no love, consideration [is] wealth”,</l>
                    <l>he is one who has the strength [and] forces by strength. </l>
                    <l>And no one is there who says “don't you fear”,</l>
                    <l rend="indent">while they pleasantly close [their] eyes,</l>
                    <l rend="indent6"> even if they don't remove [the evil] ,</l>
                    <l rend="indent2">like the people here [do] for the moon taken by the snake .</l>
                    <l>Pitiable [is] it, shame,</l>
                    <l rend="indent3">if [we] happen to leave for the place he abides there.</l>


                </lg>
            </div>
